headline: Aerospace Stock Among Names Hitting New Highs
summary: L3Harris Technologies is among the names making new highs in the stock market on Friday, rounding off a week that pushed major equity indexes to new peaks.  Enbridge is in a 5% buy zone above a 47.44 entry.  Enbridge provides pipelines and services for oil and gas transportation in Canada.
